DESCRIPTION :

This my_hunter is a game where the goal of it is to precisly shoot the bird. You have a sniper then you can shoot with one bullet every time you reaload. You have a little pet as nexus that you need to defend. After 3 bird passed you loose the game. You have 3 different difficulty. Try to be the best.

CONTROL :

Left clic : shoot
Right clic : reload
Escape : shut the window

Try to be the best and have fun !